episodes.title: Hippie Victorian SEX CULT
episodes.description:
In this video I sound rather critical of non-monogamy.  I am not.  Although it is not for me, I do not have any desire to criticize people for living their lives in whatever way seems best to them.  My criticism of this cult comes from my suspicion that it was not as consensual or innocent as it may appear at first glance.
